          "message": {
            "text": "The GET /benefits and POST /benefits routes are protected only by isLoggedIn middleware, but lack the isAdmin check. Any authenticated user can access admin-only benefits management functionality. The fix (isAdmin middleware) is present in the source code but commented out on lines 58-59."
          },
          "locations": [
